title: HOUR 1 - Kyle Shanahan, Dallas Cowboys, Albert Breer
itunes:title: HOUR 1 - Kyle Shanahan, Dallas Cowboys, Albert Breer
description:
In hour 1, Colin is impressed with Kyle Shanahans ability to turn 2nd & 3rd round draft picks into solid productive players. In the NFL Top 100 players, the vote seemed to be heavily weighed by "Cool" points rather than skill. Albert Breer joins to talk Preseason, Cowboys and more.
